summary: An ambitious and adaptable individual who thrives in dynamic environments. I am skilled in organizing myself, setting and achieving goals, and collaborating with people from diverse backgrounds. My background includes extensive experience in Marketing, Sales, and Branding across a range of industries, including NGOs, marketing agencies, FMCG, telecommunications, and hospitality services. I am comfortable working in fast-paced and agile teams, and I am able to quickly adapt to new environments. I pride myself on being a quick learner and a highly motivated team member, and I am committed to delivering results and achieving goals from day one. I am confident that my combination of soft and hard skills makes me an excellent fit for any opportunity.
